{"tid":1420951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非行動升級，真係個個都可以做到！","createTime":"2019-08-06T06:23:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T06:30:36.000Z","uid":3333,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a3c06fa9459298baf28b4d06b183e7f037bd35a3","tid":1420951,"uid":3333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:23:58.000Z","msg":"反送中運動和理非既人咁多，<br />\n出來遊行都200萬，仲未計有D係屋企怕辛苦唔出黎既，我地都要 we connect<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.<br />\n就係由今日開始擺消費<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，\b而呢個擺消費運動係有不同等級。<br />\n大家可以做以下既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 出左來打工咁多年，有少少錢就會手痕想買野，果D非必要既，新衫，新手袋，新手機。唔好買，真係有野要買，去外國網站網購！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 每星期最少搵一日，最好星期六日，唔出街，就算出街都唔買野，約朋友，另一半係屋企睇netfix又好乜都好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 月餅，台式飲品呢D可免則免，出街帶水樽！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又可以儲多D錢，又可以幫到場運動。<br />\n各位手足仲有冇野諗到同其他意見？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb776a40bd0c76477be21b49947a22b8bea2a6e5","tid":1420951,"uid":3333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fbb9f48498ab6576825c589eecc1af332ee2752","tid":1420951,"uid":3333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:24:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f276d8df54368b5caad22dfdc84c5394751a83c","tid":1420951,"uid":3333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:24:51.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"fe9d8e035d3cbac52202ed8a6349b06cf558226e","tid":1420951,"uid":3333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:25:01.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"1c0d107932b338b2d61f4b0741d7c69f44d232e5","tid":1420951,"uid":3333,"like":0,"